messages:
Name: Alexander Domínguez
Nationality: Ecuador
Date of Birth: June 5, 1987
Position: Goalkeeper
Current club: Vélez Sarsfield
Liga Profesional Argentina clubs played for: Colón, Vélez Sarsfield

Vélez Sarsfield goalkeeper Alexander Domínguez hasn't been involved in many of the club's Liga Profesional Argentina matches in 2021, making four appearances overall and accumulating 390 minutes of playing time. He has started in all four of these appearances across their 39 fixtures.

Domínguez last appeared in league action on May 16, playing 90 minutes for Vélez Sarsfield against Racing Club and keeping a clean sheet in their 4-2 defeat. He has kept three Liga Profesional Argentina clean sheets this term.
In last season's Liga Profesional Argentina, Domínguez appeared in two games for Vélez Sarsfield.
Before moving to Vélez Sarsfield in August 2021, Domínguez made 11 league appearances in total at Cerro Largo.
